{"tid":1369971,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【絕】727 元朗茶會 令屋企人都關心 一齊戰勝白色恐怖【絕】","createTime":"2019-07-26T23:58:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T03:24:15.000Z","uid":284216,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0400d8200bb541dafcff8e59f0a0243039d538e8","tid":1369971,"uid":284216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T23:58:01.000Z","msg":"作爲半個元朗人，感激佩服欣賞，仍然打算去元朗行街、追星、追悼、食老婆餅既各位<br />\n不過肉麻野唔講咁多<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>其實727，係為左向白色恐怖説不，同埋支持元朗人 </strong><br />\n<strong>要同鄉黑警講，我地唔會怕恐怖襲擊，我地會如常生活</strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">(驚係驚，但唔會影響我地要食B仔、要爬山既決心)</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>所以要揾方法將呢份<ins>向白色恐怖説不</ins>既鬥志散播出去</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n想建議一個低成本，唔理你平時係和理定葱葱子 <br />\n人人都可以做，<strong>將成件事影響力即時升級既方法 </strong><br />\n就係用愛、溫柔，做個有交帶既乖仔/ 乖女，whatsapp 又好，寫紙仔貼係雪櫃又好<br />\n同屋企人講聲你會去元朗食B仔，同埋話比佢地知點解無啦啦咁想食B仔<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">「係外國，恐怖份子搞一次事，你估真係為左要殺個一百幾十人？<br />\n其實實際係為左要恐嚇、癱瘓一萬，甚至十萬個人既生活，要每個人都活係恐懼之中<br />\n但係你又知唔知，一個地方受到恐襲後  <br />\n往往會驅使更多人正常出街，如常生活<br />\n<strong>唔比自己活係恐怖之中，唔比恐怖分子既計劃得逞</strong><br />\n<br />\n721 元朗發生既恐襲實在係太離譜，狂徒通街肆意打人<br />\n先莫論警隊同呢班人有咩關係，但係佢地的確令大家而家活係恐懼之下 <br />\n商場落閘、地鐵唔停站、公司叫員工提早收工返屋企 <br />\n出街、買送、返工、食飯，全部都提心吊膽<br />\n但係呢啲係幾咁基本既生活自由！<br />\n唔想出街既自由同人身安全都繼續被剝奪既話<br />\n就一定要做啲嘢，唔比呢種白色恐怖繼續蔓延<br />\n<br />\n所以，我今日會鼓起勇氣，同朋友一齊去元朗街頭行街，踩單車，食嘢<br />\n<strong>大大聲話比黑勢力知，<strong>我唔怕</strong></strong><br />\n不過你今日唔使擔心我<br />\n我唔係去搞事，我只係想我地呢代、下一代都可以繼續安安全全係香港自由生活<br />\n多謝你地一直以黎既愛、教導同保護<br />\n而家有啲人需要我地保護，同佢地一齊壯下膽，所以我需要去<br />\n希望你地明白」</span><br />\n<br />\n睇到呢度，唔知你明未<br />\n老豆老母最緊張就係仔女安全<br />\n你越叫佢地唔驚，佢地就越容易驚 <br />\n你可以話係悲情牌，但係而家真係去到一個位，淨係我地每個禮拜走出尼已經唔夠<br />\n<strong>我地需要盡量發大我地既影響力，令更多人肉緊埋一份</strong><br />\n而我地每個人最可以影響到既，就係自己阿爸阿媽<br />\n<br />\n所以，你唔怕老豆媽子頂唔順既話<br />\n可以直接複製貼上上面綠色段字比屋企個whatsapp group<br />\n或者你可以自己寫，總之，就要更多人關心呢單荒謬白色恐怖事件<br />\n越多人緊張，贏既機會就越大<br />\n<br />\n1999 的話唔好意思<br />\n香港人加油，萬事小心"},{"pid":"c04a0e6dceee123869ed74aca2f2f030dfb34d37","tid":1369971,"uid":284216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T23:59:12.000Z","msg":"1. 撤回逃犯條例修訂<br />\n2. 撤回 612 暴動定性<br />\n3. 成立獨立調查委員會調查警察濫權、警黑勾結<br />\n4. 釋放所有被捕示威者<br />\n5. 取消立法會功能組別 落實真雙普選"},{"pid":"764b1aa665b1875ed14d1bf4196321da326b5a2e","tid":1369971,"uid":284216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T23:59:34.000Z","msg":"香港人 <br />\n不撤不散"},{"pid":"9d746191783695ba659f485be9a4745d207d0eed","tid":1369971,"uid":284216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T00:00:30.000Z","msg":"727 唔係要清黑社會門戶<br />\n而係為左同全世界講<br />\n我地唔怕白色恐怖"},{"pid":"9ac6767eaf9fc4b0255b1b6be8458f7c10445e28","tid":1369971,"uid":210612,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T00:00:40.000Z","msg":"推土機出動<br />\n================<br />\n堅守五大訴求<br />\n勿分化勿指責&nbsp;<br />\n齊上齊落<br />\n建議大家自備物資 做流動物資站<br />\n頭盔 眼罩 口罩 毛巾 是啤衫<br />\n我無嘢講 我要見律師<br />\n對抗中聯辦恐怖治港<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"1a2d78f8c3b19803891379d3a57e07b0940ed1ce","tid":1369971,"uid":284216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T00:00:48.000Z","msg":"黒警鄉勾結可恥"},{"pid":"7470c2c3188190b155cc1dc0cedca6a26a59ce0c","tid":1369971,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T00:06:36.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"0f2ceea5e2debf42a965e31603d2df8a45562781","tid":1369971,"uid":284216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T00:10:33.000Z","msg":"香港人 你地真係好叻"},{"pid":"147877c93ef491c1d98ffe45b3907675e2ec5ef8","tid":1369971,"uid":284216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T00:10:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">向白色恐怖説不</div></strong></span>"},{"pid":"b2c76dd8ac08f1873643539d7fada41224d75656","tid":1369971,"uid":284216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T00:13:57.000Z","msg":"香港早晨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1714459b717d0e343ebb2bde0215ff0f77da3b2e","tid":1369971,"uid":284216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T00:16:32.000Z","msg":"唔該幫手推<br />\n叫埋你身邊朋友一齊做孝順有交帶仔女"},{"pid":"0fbaeb7b5e8cf6e4561dd3d811e0007e9a53629a","tid":1369971,"uid":284216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T00:47:16.000Z","msg":"好鍾意元朗<br />\n好鍾意香港"},{"pid":"11c62a9d33281632492d344be46175dbca3fbbd2","tid":1369971,"uid":287173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T00:49:21.000Z","msg":"AO EO 一定要令運動成功 ［長文］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1369805\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1369805</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4f1fbab552ec3e6ed19af7789c17ca749215738e","tid":1369971,"uid":284216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T01:11:09.000Z","msg":"不受傷 不被捕 不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰"},{"pid":"ab90a6a61623821aadc2a49def9b0d934e4db80f","tid":1369971,"uid":287173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T01:11:43.000Z","msg":"AO EO 一定要令運動成功 ［長文］<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1369805\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1369805</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0106754caa5d7cb1c8d27dedbd95d596af76be0c","tid":1369971,"uid":115977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T01:13:45.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>各位手足<br />\n萬事小心<br />\n<br />\n#一個都不能少<br />\n#727</strong></span></span>"},{"pid":"c79d4aa3c657aed9a22778f1148aeb6094a11ba2","tid":1369971,"uid":284216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T01:16:58.000Z","msg":"齊上齊落"},{"pid":"fb133c455839562eba619a64b5facbbc6c289195","tid":1369971,"uid":284216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T01:17:21.000Z","msg":"一齊去 一齊走"},{"pid":"2ef99f9ba83d785ca0b5d04a30c47c05bdb91ff0","tid":1369971,"uid":284216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T01:31:39.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"a306a7a7be31a1ae34ae87a76f24be72efd86f98","tid":1369971,"uid":284216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T01:37:03.000Z","msg":"很愛香港<br />\nwe all stand as one"},{"pid":"d7a402fd19b272415b61f17b209510652befa7a1","tid":1369971,"uid":124133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T01:45:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"324b1426daeec3460144527795b8bbc2631d997e","tid":1369971,"uid":284216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:05:12.000Z","msg":"終於會等到夢寐"},{"pid":"42310eb501b94302bab7575f0b078b5e1a423118","tid":1369971,"uid":284216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:09:31.000Z","msg":"不落單 不孤單"},{"pid":"b9abcb29cf9083694d14b2a7817ec059ae39d599","tid":1369971,"uid":265354,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:48:51.000Z","msg":"Push we should let them know"},{"pid":"898218f3dc6e28dab74d55b72e4ef87e0f079ab2","tid":1369971,"uid":263555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T03:24:15.000Z","msg":"#撤回逃犯條例<br />\n#撤回暴動定性<br />\n#撤銷所有抗爭者控罪<br />\n#追究警隊濫暴<br />\n#追究警黑勾結<br />\n#立即實行雙普選<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命 林奠贖罪"}]}